ElementDescription: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project
Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY
Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
Notes: Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.
M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

ElementDescription: My beliefs about myself often conflict with one another
Notes: 5 = Strongly Disagree; 4 = Disagree; 3 = Neither Agree nor Disagree; 2= Agree; 1 = Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: On one day I might have one opinion of myself and on another day I might have a different opinion
Notes: 5 = Strongly Disagree; 4 = Disagree; 3 = Neither Agree nor Disagree; 2= Agree; 1 = Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: I spend a lot of time wondering about what kind of person I really am
Notes: 5 = Strongly Disagree; 4 = Disagree; 3 = Neither Agree nor Disagree; 2= Agree; 1 = Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: Sometimes I feel that I am not really the person that I appear to be
Notes: 5 = Strongly Disagree; 4 = Disagree; 3 = Neither Agree nor Disagree; 2= Agree; 1 = Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: When I think about the kind of person I have been in the past, I'm not sure what I was really like
Notes: 5 = Strongly Disagree; 4 = Disagree; 3 = Neither Agree nor Disagree; 2= Agree; 1 = Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: I seldom experience conflict between the different aspects of my personality
Notes: 1 = Strongly Disagree; 2 = Disagree; 3 = Neither Agree nor Disagree; 4 = Agree; 5 = Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: Sometimes I think I know other people better than I know myself
Notes: 5 = Strongly Disagree; 4 = Disagree; 3 = Neither Agree nor Disagree; 2= Agree; 1 = Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: My beliefs about myself seem to change very frequently
Notes: 5 = Strongly Disagree; 4 = Disagree; 3 = Neither Agree nor Disagree; 2= Agree; 1 = Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: If I were asked to describe my personality, my description might end up being different from one day to another day
Notes: 5 = Strongly Disagree; 4 = Disagree; 3 = Neither Agree nor Disagree; 2= Agree; 1 = Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: Even if I wanted to, I don't think I could tell someone what I'm really like
Notes: 5 = Strongly Disagree; 4 = Disagree; 3 = Neither Agree nor Disagree; 2= Agree; 1 = Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: In general, I have a clear sense of who I am and what I am
Notes: 1 = Strongly Disagree; 2 = Disagree; 3 = Neither Agree nor Disagree; 4 = Agree; 5 = Strongly Agree

ElementDescription: It is often hard for me to make up my mind about things because I don't really know what I want
Notes: 5 = Strongly Disagree; 4 = Disagree; 3 = Neither Agree nor Disagree; 2= Agree; 1 = Strongly Agree
